{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/configure-sublime-text-3/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Fei"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"01716942-6ff3-57ab-acc3-89cb08370199","excerpt":"下文基于 64 位 Windows 7 SP1 系统，不保证其它平台通用。 下载与安装 下载 Sublimte Text 3 安装，勾上  安装 Package Control 同时按下 Ctrl + ` 输入 安装 Soada 主题 同时按下 Ctrl + Shift + p…","html":"<p>下文基于 64 位 Windows 7 SP1 系统，不保证其它平台通用。</p>\n<h3>下载与安装</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>下载 <a href=\"http://www.sublimetext.com/3\">Sublimte Text 3</a></li>\n<li>安装，勾上 <code class=\"language-text\">Add to explorer context menu</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h3>安装 Package Control</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>同时按下 <kbd>Ctrl + `</kbd></li>\n<li>输入</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> urllib<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>request<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>os<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>hashlib<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> h <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'7183a2d3e96f11eeadd761d777e62404'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'e330c659d4bb41d3bdf022e94cab3cd0'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> pf <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Package Control.sublime-package'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> ipp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> sublime<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>installed_packages_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> urllib<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>request<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>install_opener<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> urllib<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>request<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>build_opener<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> urllib<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>request<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ProxyHandler<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> by <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> urllib<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>request<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>urlopen<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token string\">'http://sublime.wbond.net/'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> pf<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>replace<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">' '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'%20'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>read<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> dh <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> hashlib<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sha256<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>by<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>hexdigest<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Error validating download (got %s instead of %s), please try manual install'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dh<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> h<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> dh <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> h <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>os<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>join<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> ipp<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> pf<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'wb'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>write<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>by<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>安装 Soada 主题</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>同时按下 <kbd>Ctrl + Shift + p</kbd>，输入 <code class=\"language-text\">Install Package</code>，回车</li>\n<li>输入 <code class=\"language-text\">theme soda</code>，回车</li>\n<li>菜单栏选择 <code class=\"language-text\">Preferences -&gt; Settings - User</code></li>\n<li>加入 <code class=\"language-text\">&quot;theme&quot;: &quot;Soda Dark.sublime-theme&quot;</code></li>\n<li>重启 Sublime Text 3</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>安装代码配色</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>下载 <a href=\"http://buymeasoda.github.com/soda-theme/extras/colour-schemes.zip\">colour-schemes.zip</a></li>\n<li>菜单栏选择 <code class=\"language-text\">Preferences -&gt; Browse Packages...</code></li>\n<li>解压下载文件到 <code class=\"language-text\">user</code> 目录</li>\n<li>菜单栏选择 <code class=\"language-text\">Preferences -&gt; Color Scheme -&gt; User -&gt; Monokai Soda</code> 启用配色</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>安装 ConvertToUTF8</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>同时按下 <kbd>Ctrl + Shift + p</kbd>，输入 `Install Package’，回车</li>\n<li>输入 `ConvertToUTF8’，回车</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>更改用户配置</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token string\">\"font_size\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">11</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"tab_size\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"trim_trailing_white_space_on_save\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"translate_tabs_to_spaces\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>关联 Powershell</h3>\n<p>最终实现命令行中输入 <code class=\"language-text\">sub test.txt</code> 自动打开 Sublime Text 3 编辑该文件。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>以管理员方式运行 Powershell，输入 <code class=\"language-text\">Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned</code> 用以获得脚本执行权限</li>\n<li>输入 <code class=\"language-text\">Test-Path $profile</code> 检查配置文件是否存在</li>\n<li>若返回 <code class=\"language-text\">False</code>，输入 <code class=\"language-text\">ni -path $profile -type file -force</code> 创建配置文件</li>\n<li>输入 <code class=\"language-text\">notepad $profile</code> 编辑该配置文件，加入 <code class=\"language-text\">Set-Alias sub &quot;C:\\Program Files\\Sublime Text 3\\sublime_text.exe&quot;</code></li>\n<li>保存该文件，重启 Poweshell</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"调教 Sublime Text 3","date":"2014-05-25","description":"基于 64 位 Windows 7 SP1 系统，调教 Sublime Text 3。"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/configure-sublime-text-3/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/google-calendar-sync-error/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Google Calendar Sync出错"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/configure-git-vagrant/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"开发环境配置"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","4265873673"]}